Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95116,95116}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:44.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101331,104584}Too bad about that contest,\Nhuh, Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:49.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104584,109464}Yeah, and Rina too, but I heard\Nyou did pretty good. Right, Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.17,0:01:55.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110173,115428}They both didn't make it.\NThat means they weren't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:02:00.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:117180,120767}You're right.\NAlso, too bad, Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:04.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120767,124020}How stupid of you to let St. Tail\Nget away when you had her trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:06.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124479,126773}Why, you! Back then—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:08.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127273,128441}Back then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:09.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:128441,129359}Back then—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.35,0:02:13.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129359,133613}I just remembered.\NI have things to do. I'll see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133613,135156}Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:18.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136949,138743}Back then, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:22.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139285,142955}Meimi, don't rub it in.\NHe's really hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:27.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:144207,147210}{\i1}I don't know what got\Ninto me that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:42.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157345,162141}{\i1}Asuka Jr., I swear\NI'll get you to notice me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:48.14,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:163976,168147}The Mayor's Ambition!\NStealing a Swan (Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171693,173611}Excuse me, Mayor Morinaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174404,176572}The sculpture from\NSakuraoka has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:03:00.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177240,180827}Thank you.\NHave them bring it up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:02.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180827,182787}What sculpture, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:07.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183663,187792}Rina, you've heard of\NIchiro Kanoh, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:10.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188292,190795}Yes, the renowned sculptor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:14.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191963,194257}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194257,196259}Is this one of his sculptures?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:21.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196801,201723}This is The Swan,\None of his first pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:25.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202140,205685}Wow, it's beautiful.\NIt's crystal, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:30.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206894,210314}It belongs to the city of Sakuraoka,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210314,212900}but the mayor's lent it\Nto us for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:38.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213609,218698}I want our citizens to see this,\Nso I'm displaying it at the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218698,220116}It looks expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.82,0:03:44.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220825,224620}By the way, Rina, what did you\Nwant to see me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:50.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228332,230126}Hmm? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:55.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234380,235757}It's about Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:04:02.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235757,242638}Ah, Asuka Jr.… You've been fond of him\Nfrom the time you moved to this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:04.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242638,244223}What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:06.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244223,246058}Asuka Jr.…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:10.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247059,250062}He has no intention\Nof arresting St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:12.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250438,252315}Hmm? What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:18.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253065,258780}I saw him. He had her\Ntrapped the other night,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:20.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258780,260948}but he let go of her hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:31.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269290,271793}He let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272502,275129}You're sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275129,277256}Letting him remain\Non the case is a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:42.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278132,282970}You must take him off\Nall of St. Tail's investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:48.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285890,288684}I understand.\NLet me think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289602,291687}Yes, Uncle. You know what's best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:58.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295900,298194}Has The Swan reached Seika City?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:02.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298486,302114}Yes, we just confirmed it\Nwith Mayor Morinaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:03.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302114,303658}Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:08.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304575,308371}I guess you could say the stage is set.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:10.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308371,310623}Yabe, when did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:16.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310998,316087}Mr. Okajima, you are truly\Na corrupt mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:20.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316087,320591}You lend the crystal to Seika,\Nthen have it stolen and fill your pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:23.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321759,323427}Just call me smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:31.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326097,331727}That's why I hired an experienced\Nthief like you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:37.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334355,337650}I'm aware of that.\NIf it's stolen from Seika,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:42.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337650,342446}the responsibility's not yours,\Nand you get the crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:47.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342446,347076}On top of that, Seika has to pay you\Na lot in compensation, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:50.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347618,350663}Never mind.\NHow are your preparations going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:53.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:350663,353291}Don't worry.\NEverything's taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:57.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353916,357420}Do a good job getting it.\NI'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361090,362508}Good morning, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:05.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363009,365011}Ryoko, Kyoko, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:09.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365428,369098}Did you read the newspaper?\NI was absolutely shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:15.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369557,375771}"Tomorrow evening, I'll go to the art\Nmuseum to steal The Swan. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:19.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375771,379775}– She's being very bold this time.\N– She sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:24.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380401,384739}{\i1}What's going on?\NI didn't make this announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:27.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384739,387992}What are you gonna do?\NShe's making a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:31.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388326,391412}– It's obvious—\N– Obvious she'll get away with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:34.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391412,394582}Shut up! I'm not letting her\Nget away purposely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:35.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394582,395458}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:40.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396125,400796}If you keep letting her get away,\Nthe Mayor will lose patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400796,402798}I know! This time for sure—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:46.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402798,406636}This time she's not getting away!\NWe hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:49.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406636,409639}You guys aren't human!\NI'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409639,411933}Oh, save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:56.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412642,416437}{\i1}Chase her to your heart's content\Nfor the time being, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:07:00.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417104,420942}{\i1}Because very soon now\Nyou'll never be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:14.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430201,434246}My, so you came here\Nall the way from Sakuraoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:18.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434747,438626}Yes, because I heard\NThe Swan was here in Seika.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:20.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438626,440544}So you came here to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440544,441629}No, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:23.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442713,443881}Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444715,447843}I know the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:31.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447843,451639}St. Tail's announcement\Nin today's paper is a fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:32.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451639,452765}It's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:35.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452765,455351}Calm down.\NWho are you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:41.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456435,461107}I'm a maid. I work for\NMr. Okajima, Sakuraoka's mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:45.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461107,465444}I heard the mayor and\Nanother man plotting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:52.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467697,472785}After I steal it, you'd better sell it\Noverseas before they trace it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:56.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473035,476372}I'll do that.\NYou'll help me, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:07:58.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476914,478541}You can count on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:02.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479041,482670}I thought of going right to the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:06.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482670,486048}but I'm a live-in maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:10.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486048,490261}If I were to lose my job,\NI'd have nowhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490261,492930}And so you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:18.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493639,498728}Forgive me.\NI just had to talk to someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498728,500521}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:26.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502314,506152}Don't worry.\NI'm sure the Lord will guide you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:39.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516120,519415}{\i1}What did that article\Nin this morning's paper mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:43.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519415,523878}{\i1}Seira says she didn't know about it,\Nand I didn't do it. Could it be a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:50.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530051,530843}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532344,534096}Can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:58.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534638,538059}What were you doing?\NIs this another experiment in suspension?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:04.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539351,544440}The last one was a failure.\NBut now this time, watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:10.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548861,550946}– See?\N– Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:27.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564668,567797}– How did you do that?\N– I'm glad you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.79,0:09:33.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567797,573636}When I push the switch on my wrist, the motor\Non my hip extends and retracts the wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:38.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575930,578641}Wow, it's fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:42.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579266,582144}And it can even do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:49.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585898,589610}Instant transit.\NLook how fast I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590528,592071}Look how fast I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:56.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595241,596450}That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:59.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597326,599703}And you can do something like—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:02.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599703,602081}Meimi, dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:04.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602081,604917}Why, Dad,\NI thought you were outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:08.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605584,608045}He came in through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:08.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608045,608671}Not really—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:11.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608671,611590}What were you thinking,\Nsneaking into your daughter's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:13.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611590,613300}You see, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:15.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613300,615886}Did you say dinner? Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616512,618180}How childish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:27.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625062,627273}Then that announcement…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:32.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627273,632319}Yes. I'm sure Mayor Okajima told\Nthat Mr. Yabe to have it printed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633112,635990}They want St. Tail to get blamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:38.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635990,638784}What terrible people!\NThey won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:44.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639285,644039}Is there some way we can get The Swan\Nbefore that Yabe steals it, Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:48.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644373,648502}Of course there is! I'm going\Nto the museum tomorrow night, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:56.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654508,656760}Have you finished\Nsetting up the display?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658137,660472}– Mr. Mayor.\N– Yes, we're almost finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:06.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661640,666437}Because it's a crystal swan,\Nwe put it in the setting of a lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:12.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667062,672401}Asuka Jr. suggested we put a lake\Naround it so no one can get too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:15.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673068,675821}Naturally, security will be very tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:20.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675821,680117}I intend to spend the night in the space\Nbetween the case and lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:23.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680492,683996}You personally?\NCan't we use a security camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:28.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683996,688209}Well, machinery\Ncan be reprogrammed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:31.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688209,691587}She's not getting away this time.\NI intend to capture her myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:36.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694215,696800}{\i1}He has no intention\Nof arresting St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:40.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698427,700471}Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:48.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703807,708729}Since I already announced yesterday\Nabout the exhibit, I can't cancel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:52.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709188,712233}I'm counting on you.\NDon't let me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:54.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713067,714068}I won't!
Comment: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:55.73,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:715736,715736}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:00.74,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:720741,720741}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:22.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738425,742179}Asuka Jr., I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:34.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752731,754149}{\i1}Asuka Jr.…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:37.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755067,757152}{\i1}It's your own fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757152,758612}{\i1}Not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:50.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765786,770749}All right, men, it's almost time,\Nso please take your positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770749,772209}Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:08.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784722,788475}I'm ready for you, St. Tail.\NTonight's the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:16.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793188,796942}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:22.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801905,802948}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:26.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805326,806618}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808579,810873}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:49.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827139,829141}Ruby, you rascal, you followed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:54.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829850,834855}Tonight is important.\NMy reputation is at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:58.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836940,838942}Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:01.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838942,841570}I'll take care of Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:03.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841570,843614}Come on, Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:05.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843614,845074}Thank you, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:10.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845866,850537}I'll keep The Swan until Yabe is arrested,\Nthen return it to the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852456,853499}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:19.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855709,859505}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871100,873102}{\i1}I'm ready for you, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:38.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874686,878774}{\i1}Just touch this case and I'll nab you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:42.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878774,882861}{\i1}That's right. I'll have no problem\Nif I catch you in the act.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:14.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:911640,914143}I need you to take a little nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:41.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937624,941670}{\i1}So that's it.\NGood, Yabe's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:19.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976705,979124}– She's here!\N– Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:24.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979583,984421}{\i1}Wait, take it easy.\NYou've got to catch her in the act!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:27.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:984421,987591}{\i1}It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:34.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992262,994097}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:37.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994932,997559}Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999102,1000437}Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:17:01.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017287,1021166}{\i1}They're all asleep.\NI've got to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022292,1024169}{\i1}What a fitting display.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026046,1027923}{\i1}She's here! It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:12.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031343,1032678}{\i1}I got her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034137,1036640}You're not taking that, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:19.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036974,1039101}{\i1}So this is where he was!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:24.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042437,1044815}Don't fight it! Give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:35.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052739,1055784}You're not getting away, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:45.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064126,1065544}{\i1}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:54.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072217,1074261}Rats! She's a decoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076763,1078265}{\i1}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:02.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080767,1082394}{\i1}Ow, my leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:05.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084396,1085689}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092070,1093572}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:14.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093572,1094865}Uh? Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:19.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095616,1099453}– The sculpture's been stolen!\N– What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099453,1100912}Where's Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101872,1103206}{\i1}Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:36.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112966,1116011}{\i1}Aw, shoot! Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:47.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125479,1127981}Hold it! Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130901,1132944}That's a straight road! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:02.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138784,1142245}{\i1}I'm not letting her\Nget away this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171400,1173110}{\i1}You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180826,1182411}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.96,0:20:00.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195966,1200971}{\i1}That's funny.\NI didn't know St. Tail used cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:07.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203348,1207436}Thank you, St. Tail!\NWho'd have thought it'd go so smoothly?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:10.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207978,1210564}That fake ad in the paper\Nwas bullseye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.56,0:20:11.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1210564,1211690}{\i1}What'd he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:23.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219656,1223493}{\i1}I finally made it up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:27.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223493,1227372}{\i1}Asuka Jr., I never thought\Nit'd turn out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:32.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229207,1232502}{\i1}Asuka Jr., be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:36.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234588,1236465}{\i1}Come back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:48.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245140,1248518}{\i1}Asuka Jr., come back safely!
